ji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n比啲信心呀巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n考咩車種<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a33aecc809cef5f15761c9dd8ab6927cb1e76f3","tid":7152,"uid":31336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T17:39:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>一月考    預左考兩次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n比啲信心呀巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n考咩車種<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n棍van <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />    轉波係好玩    但唔合格就收皮"},{"pid":"b450edce943cd8ccb236394b58000ed7e35d09bb","tid":7152,"uid":390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T17:41:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>一月考    預左考兩次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n比啲信心呀巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n考咩車種<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n棍van <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />    轉波係好玩    但唔合格就收皮</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都擔心緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62523de2f27725add0b1863a3f3be2494a3ed5d1","tid":7152,"uid":2764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T18:31:17.000Z","msg":"9月中 丙部pass左<br />\n行靠背壟<br />\n呢個試場其實算係咁<br />\n雖然又窄又多人多車<br />\n但你望多d鏡同望遠d就ok<br />\n就算肥都唔好肥晒2part呀<br />\n得天光道係泊L位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c2a030875ae5b1942ff626653569b7b8b6688f9","tid":7152,"uid":6283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T06:32:29.000Z","msg":"考果陣 鎮定d 我都係岩岩pass幾日 <br />\n行靠背壟道 個考官話轉左轉右 你就禮貌既回應個考官 下午放學時間就自求多福 因為好多校巴 死車 咩車都有 盲毛又有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  盡量唔好太接近車 遠少少都無所謂 望多d鏡 動作大少少 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我考8:45"},{"pid":"fcd48920f766edcb2df4eed2a8e0e3a49787ec14","tid":7152,"uid":31336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T06:34:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>考果陣 鎮定d 我都係岩岩pass幾日 <br />\n行靠背壟道 個考官話轉左轉右 你就禮貌既回應個考官 下午放學時間就自求多福 因為好多校巴 死車 咩車都有 盲毛又有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  盡量唔好太接近車 遠少少都無所謂 望多d鏡 動作大少少 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我考8:45</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我考4點  校巴 死車 盲毛 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  自求多福  <br />\n希望下次揀個好時間"},{"pid":"73c31ee9c7cb5ce947c22873e17c7df5eda0161f","tid":7152,"uid":6283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T06:42:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>考果陣 鎮定d 我都係岩岩pass幾日 <br />\n行靠背壟道 個考官話轉左轉右 你就禮貌既回應個考官 下午放學時間就自求多福 因為好多校巴 死車 咩車都有 盲毛又有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  盡量唔好太接近車 遠少少都無所謂 望多d鏡 動作大少少 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我考8:45</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我考4點  校巴 死車 盲毛 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  自求多福  <br />\n希望下次揀個好時間</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n盡量慢慢黎 個官唔會吹你 真係天時地利人和<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之前學3-4點左右 係好多人亂咁沖出馬路 睇定d"},{"pid":"f48d0db8b142d65d9d4655575feaa3a6a28c8d2d","tid":7152,"uid":4396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T07:02:16.000Z","msg":"我12月考<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 學左20節（一節45分鐘）好驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8636dc199a5985ec49020582d92a72ce14a83743","tid":7152,"uid":390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T09:28:56.000Z","msg":"Push<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n天光道嘅入嚟喇喂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e49e3f8df12313f4e1f0716b1529cc4e06c01a15","tid":7152,"uid":24938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T12:37:30.000Z","msg":"八月個陣7 ticks pass 左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n覺得揸車最緊要唔好怯<br />\n怯就輸左九成<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59003c60e439ac1b722287862e9a87039c126922","tid":7152,"uid":390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T15:38:30.000Z","msg":"未開始學總係好大期待<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n遲下再黎賽後包膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8fc2abaf653da48e211a1435b0261f65a9d6c4fe","tid":7152,"uid":16373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T15:41:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>2月考 未學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都2月考又未學，不過我係忠義街"},{"pid":"83a718457f89f1290ff38b23efd3a492cb83cb62","tid":7152,"uid":263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T02:22:40.000Z","msg":"6月考 天光撚<br />\n完全唔熟車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n諗緊幾時開始上堂好"},{"pid":"13028d738fde82e3ee086ea3cb973688a18311dc","tid":7152,"uid":6710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T03:58:37.000Z","msg":"3月考here<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"347ce2185d03466fba2430ae57dad4301ce434ef","tid":7152,"uid":5911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cit